<TITLE>Description
</TITLE>
<PARA>
<FUNCTION>sigvec</FUNCTION> is made obsolete by 
<FUNCTION>sigaction</FUNCTION>.
</PARA><PARA>
Under Linux, <FUNCTION>sigvec</FUNCTION> is <EMPHASIS>#define</EMPHASIS>d 
to <FUNCTION>sigaction</FUNCTION>, and provides at best a rough 
approximation of the <ACRONYM>BSD</ACRONYM> <FUNCTION>sigvec</FUNCTION> 
interface.
</PARA>
</REFSECT1>

